This is a collection of miscellaneous stuff that is version-controlled and
that doesn't fit anywhere else.

bin:
  Scripts that go into the "bin" directory put into my $PATH.

build:
  Scripts to customize software I build from source.

gfx:
  Art-work and other graphics files.

rcfiles:
  "Dot-files" and other runtime-configuration files.

templates:
  Templates for various things (bash-scripts, Makefiles, etc.).
